LAGOS – The People’s Democratic Party’s Presidential candidate in the forthcoming 2023 general elections, Atiku Abubakar (GCON) has lauded the Supreme Court ruling on section 84 (12). According to him in a tweet on his official twitter handle @atiku, the ruling affirms his position on the independence of the Nigerian Judiciary. He wrote, “The ruling of the Supreme Court on Section 84 (12) is commendable. It affirms my position of the independence of the judiciary and the other arms of government, namely the legislature and the executive, which is the bedrock for the development of any nation.” See tweet below;